---
title: The Sesame Slam Crispy Sesame Chicken Schnitzel Burger, Fries, Pickled Cucumber Slaw and Hoisin Mayo
description: Super indulgent and packed full of flavour, The Sesame Slam is your favourite burger brought to the next level.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R38_W06_UK_SCB17486-3_Main_F2_low-769d8e23.jpg
